menu "Home Key Provisioner"

config HOMEKEY_FACTORY_ISSUER_PUBKEY_HEX
    string "Factory issuer Ed25519 public key (hex)"
    default ""
    help
        Optional 32-byte Ed25519 issuer public key encoded as 64 hex characters.
        When set, the ota_1 Home Key provisioner will automatically seed this
        issuer into shared reader data before Apple Home starts endpoint
        enrollment over the HomeKit NFCAccess service.

        This is required because Apple's device-credential enrollment TLVs only
        carry an issuer identifier, not the issuer public key itself.

endmenu
